hich one-pager section provides which info (Binary, CLI Flags, Gaps & Limitations, Config Preservation)\\n- **Fallback**: \\\"If something is missing from the one-pager, search external docs — but update `AGENT.md`\\\"\\n\\n### 3. `implementer.md` — References one-pager for agent-specific info\\n- **Prerequisites**: Points to `AGENT.md`\\n- **Step 2**: Reads `AGENT.md` first, uses its sections to pick the best reference implementation\\n- **Step 3**: Each stub file references the specific one-pager section it should use (types.go → \\\"Hook input\\\", lifecycle.go → \\\"Hook names\\\" table, hooks.go → \\\"Config file\\\", transcript.go → \\\"Transcript\\\")\\n- **Steps 4-12**: Added standing instruction about checking `AGENT.md` first and updating it with new discoveries\\n- **Step 10**: References one-pager instead of \\\"research report\\\"\\n\\n### 4. `SKILL.md` — Updated phase descriptions\\n- **Phase 1**: Describes external-only focus and one-pager as the output artifact\\n- **Phase 2**: Notes it uses the one-pager for agent-specific information\\n- **Phase 3**: Notes it reads internal docs and uses the one-pager for agent-specific details\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":1811,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":87284,\"output_tokens\":717,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":1811,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYXg21HsoTNGV7xBrzkp1\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"ff490ff2-6569-48c4-8cd2-490d4cc0618a\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-27T01:04:01.298Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"ff490ff2-6569-48c4-8cd2-490d4cc0618a\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/wt/kiro-oneshot\",\"sessionId\":\"46c073e8-9109-4faf-bd0b-fe9c0209ac96\",\"version\":\"2.1.61\",\